{"id":69718,"title":"Ganglion cyst arising from the first metacarpophalangeal joint in an adolescent.","abstract":"Pediatric ganglion cyst of the hand is a rare entity. Its incidence is even lower in those arising from the metacarpophalangeal (MP) joint. We herein report the first known case of a ganglion cyst of the first MP joint in a 14-year-old boy. Pathogenesis, diagnosis and treatment are discussed.","date":"2014-10-13","categories":"Neoplasms","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25306798","annotations":[{"name":"Joint","weight":0.69413,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joint"},{"name":"Cyst","weight":0.633579,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cyst"},{"name":"Incidence (epidemiology)","weight":0.574584,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Incidence_(epidemiology)"},{"name":"Pediatrics","weight":0.525309,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pediatrics"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.353863,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Pathogenesis","weight":0.325655,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pathogenesis"},{"name":"Ganglion","weight":0.222846,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ganglion"},{"name":"Adolescence","weight":0.129065,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adolescence"},{"name":"Member of Parliament","weight":0.116551,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Member_of_Parliament"},{"name":"Diagnosis","weight":0.100374,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diagnosis"},{"name":"Ganglion cyst","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ganglion_cyst"},{"name":"Metacarpophalangeal joint","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Metacarpophalangeal_joint"},{"name":"Entity","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Entity"}]}
